sequenceDiagram
    participant App as AAOS App
    participant Backend as Car Pay-in Backend
    participant CpRedis as carpayin-redis
    participant DB as Car Pay-in DB
    participant PMS as Parking PMS
    participant PmsRedis as pms-redis
    participant PMSDB as PMS DB
    participant LPR as LPR Camera
    participant Barrier as Barrier Controller
    participant SQS as AWS SQS
    participant Lambda as AWS Lambda
    participant IoT as AWS IoT Core

    App->>Backend: POST /parking/navigate {lot_id}
    Backend->>DB: Read vehicles (car_id from token)
    Backend->>DB: Check active vehicle_billing_keys
    Backend->>CpRedis: Save parking_pre_notify:{lot_id}:{plate}

    Backend->>PMS: POST /parking/pre-register {lot_id, plate}
    PMS->>PmsRedis: Save pre_reg:{lot_id}:{plate} TTL 1h
    PMS-->>Backend: Return ok
    Backend-->>App: Return registered

    LPR->>PMS: Detect plate at entry gate
    PMS->>Barrier: HTTP POST /open (entry, all cars)
    PMS->>PMSDB: INSERT parking_sessions (all cars)
    PMS->>PmsRedis: Save parking_session:{lot_id}:{plate} status=active TTL 72h
    PMS->>PmsRedis: Check pre_reg:{lot_id}:{plate}
    PMS->>PmsRedis: Delete pre_reg key (consume)
    PMS->>PMS: Sign raw body with PMS_WEBHOOK_SECRET
    PMS-->>Backend: POST /webhook/entry with X-Webhook headers

    Backend->>Backend: Verify raw body HMAC and timestamp
    Backend->>CpRedis: Read parking_pre_notify:{lot_id}:{plate}
    Backend->>DB: INSERT parking_sessions
    Backend->>CpRedis: Delete parking_pre_notify:{lot_id}:{plate}
    Backend->>SQS: Publish parking.confirmed event
    SQS->>Lambda: Trigger notification Lambda
    Lambda->>IoT: Publish to car/{car_id}/parking topic
    IoT-->>App: Entry notification → parked=true
